trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> class adds an entry to the directory.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> 클래스는 디렉터리에 항목을 추가합니다.

trans-unit.source: The request may be added to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument> or it can be used as the parameter for <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.SendRequest%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 요청에 추가할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument> 에 대 한 매개 변수로 사용할 수 있습니다 또는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.SendRequest%2A>합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.#ctor" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> class.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.#ctor" /> 생성자는 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> 클래스의 인스턴스를 만듭니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.#ctor" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> class.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.#ctor" /> 생성자는 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> 클래스의 인스턴스를 만듭니다.

trans-unit.source: The <c>distinguishedName</c> of the new object in the directory.
trans-unit.target: 디렉터리에 있는 새 개체의 <c>distinguishedName</c>입니다.

trans-unit.source: An array, of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttribute" /> objects, that contains the attributes for this object.
trans-unit.target: 이 개체의 특성을 포함하는 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttribute" /> 개체의 배열입니다.

trans-unit.source: This parameter may be <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 이 매개 변수는 <see langword="null" />일 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.#ctor(System.String,System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttribute[])" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> class using the specified distinguished name and attributes.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.#ctor(System.String,System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttribute[])" /> 생성자는 지정된 고유 이름과 특성을 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> 클래스의 인스턴스를 만듭니다.

trans-unit.source: The <c>distinguishedName</c> of the new object in the directory.
trans-unit.target: 디렉터리에 있는 새 개체의 <c>distinguishedName</c>입니다.

trans-unit.source: The object class for this object.
trans-unit.target: 이 개체의 개체 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: If this parameter is <see langword="null" />, an exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: 이 매개 변수가 <see langword="null" />이면 예외가 throw됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.#ctor(System.String,System.String)" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> class using the specified <paramref name="distinguishedName" /> and the object class.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.#ctor(System.String,System.String)" /> 생성자는 지정된 <paramref name="distinguishedName" />과 개체 클래스를 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> 클래스의 인스턴스를 만듭니다.

trans-unit.source: This value can be modified after this constructor is called.
trans-unit.target: 이 생성자를 호출한 후에이 값을 수정할 수 있습니다.
